      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why i'm typing this. everything just feels so heavy. i spent 6 years on this research and now the lab is shutting down and the funding is gone. it feels like my whole life was a lie. i'm just so tired of fighting to stay afloat. i just want everything to stop. i just want some actual peace.",
