      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that \"path forward\" thing... it feels like such a joke. any path forward just means more of the same fighting, more of the same failing, and more of the same exhaustion. i feel like i'm just running on a treadmill that's going too fast and i'm about to fall off. i don't want to \"find a path,\" i just want to be able to rest without feeling the pressure of everything constantly crushing me.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
